title: Ryno, Sarge and Doctor K: A look back at Mets-Cubs in '84
text: > Sports Ryno, Sarge and Doctor K: A look back at Mets-Cubs in '84 FILE - In this Sept. 8, 1984 file photo, Chicago Cubs pitcher Rick Suteliffe throws in the second inning of a baseball game against the New York Mets at Shea Stadium in New York. The Mets and Cubs, who are playing each other in Game 3 of the NL Championship Series on Tuesday, Oct. 20, 2015, had a memorable race for the NL East title in 1984. (AP Photo/Ray Stubblebine, File)
